-    - CI config (`.github/workflows/*`, `.gitlab-ci.yml`, etc.) — the de-facto PR proof gate
-    - analyzer/architecture configs (`.dependency-cruiser.*`, `archunit`, Roslyn `.editorconfig`/`*.ruleset`, `codeql/`, JSON-schema files)
